---
title: Rigatoni Al Forno with Roasted Eggplant, Fresh Mozzarella, and Basil
description: Oven-baked pasta (pasta al forno) is Italian comfort food at its finest. Even if you don’t have a Nonna, you can still appreciate the nostalgic warmth this dish brings to the table. Gooey mozzarella makes this dish irresistible.
